  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/19af32f1b8e6cfa46c617e3c4c78dcee.poster.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/19af32f1b8e6cfa46c617e3c4c78dcee.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/19af32f1b8e6cfa46c617e3c4c78dcee.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>An online, PvP, first-person shooter that combines fast-paced combat and roguelike upgrades. <br><br>Hop into your suit and glide around the maps with buttery smooth movement. Every match is a wild ride where your upgrade choices can make or break you. It's like a fast-paced game of chess, but instead of kings and queens, you've got lasers and explosions.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>KEY FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> FPS with Roguelike upgrades<br></li><li> 4 suits, each with unique weapons, abilities, and upgrades<br></li><li> Roguelite progression tree for each suit<br></li><li> Early Access Release Game Modes: 4v4 Wipeout, 16v16 Warmup<br></li><li> Custom Map Editor</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/50f51de0ce828a0e5e8a38cf8e558997.poster.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/50f51de0ce828a0e5e8a38cf8e558997.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/50f51de0ce828a0e5e8a38cf8e558997.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CHUNK - Can take a hit</strong></h2>Unique Weapons: Rocket Launcher, Echo HMG, Shaft<br>Unique Abilities: Leap Slam, Shield Dome<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EGGBOT - Heart of gold</strong></h2>Unique Weapons: Blue-J XB, Banshee, Spectre<br>Unique Abilities: Bolt, Teleport To Friend<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>SCOUT - Catch me if you can</strong></h2>Unique Weapons: Heavy Sniper, Ironclad, SB-34 MG<br>Unique Abilities: Hookshot, Healing Grenade<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>TINY - Big and small</strong></h2>Unique Weapons: Grenade Launcher, Blaster, Wolfhound<br>Unique Abilities: Big/Small, Punch/Uppercut<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/f3bc1e58539bd110874927f008f306d0.avif?t=1721130299\" width=616 height=268 /></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/03db77cd651e187d422bd2c597c8348f.poster.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/03db77cd651e187d422bd2c597c8348f.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/03db77cd651e187d422bd2c597c8348f.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>EARLY ACCESS RELEASE GAME MODES</strong></h2>4v4 Wipeout: Respawn timers increase with every death. Eliminate the entire opposite team to win the round.<br><br>16v16 Warmup: Large scale team based shootout. Try out characters and weapons and use opponents for target practice.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/00f5ee3364dcc3b76f983c37e0f7036d.poster.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/00f5ee3364dcc3b76f983c37e0f7036d.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/00f5ee3364dcc3b76f983c37e0f7036d.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOM MAP EDITOR</strong></h2>Create your own maps using the in-game map editor, the same editor used by our dev team. Then play these community maps with your friends in custom lobbies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/fd249df2df227baa2720f0523385ece0.poster.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/fd249df2df227baa2720f0523385ece0.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/fd249df2df227baa2720f0523385ece0.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>OH YOU'RE STILL HERE</strong></h2>Here's a sneakpeek of the weebles hard at work. We also post more details of our development process on Discord. ;)<br><br>",
