ter.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/00f5ee3364dcc3b76f983c37e0f7036d.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/00f5ee3364dcc3b76f983c37e0f7036d.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>CUSTOM MAP EDITOR</strong></h2>Create your own maps using the in-game map editor, the same editor used by our dev team. Then play these community maps with your friends in custom lobbies.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/fd249df2df227baa2720f0523385ece0.poster.avif?t=1721130299\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/fd249df2df227baa2720f0523385ece0.webm?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2805060/extras/fd249df2df227baa2720f0523385ece0.mp4?t=1721130299\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>OH YOU'RE STILL HERE</strong></h2>Here's a sneakpeek of the weebles hard at work. We also post more details of our development process on Discord. ;)<br><br>",
